node.text:
When painting a beehive there are a few things you should keep in mind. 
🐝Paint with none-toxic, latex paint with low VOCs
🐝 it is said that a bee’s favorite colors are violet, purple and blue
🐝 don’t paint on the inside or walkways of the beehive
🌻 Check out this video for more beehive painting tips and bee facts!
🍯 if you are interested in beekeeping yourself there are a few spots open in the beekeeping club that I’ve joined! Check it out at @sarvodayafarms

node.text:
A little peek into my beekeeping class! 🐝✨ 
Today, we removed some empty frames from a new section of the beehive to coat with honey. Honey attracts the bees to these frames and encourages them to build honeycomb there! Fingers crossed that it works 🤞🏼✨🐝
Looking ing at a full honeycomb with bees busily working and buzzing around is probably one of the most beautiful things I’ve ever seen! 
Check out where I take my beekeeping classes! @sarvodayafarms

Sand temperature determines the gender of baby sea turtles 🐢✨
Cooler sand produces more males, while warmer sand produces more females. 
So if there happens to be any sea turtle eggs around me what SEX do you think they would be? 😜

node.text:
When painting a beehive there are a few things you should keep in mind. 
🐝Paint with none-toxic, latex paint with low VOCs
🐝 it is said that a bee’s favorite colors are violet, purple and blue
🐝 don’t paint on the inside or walkways of the beehive
🌻 Check out this video for more beehive painting tips and bee facts!
🍯 if you are interested in beekeeping yourself there are a few spots open in the beekeeping club that I’ve joined! Check it out at @sarvodayafarms
